title: Comedians in Cars Getting Coffee - S03E07 - Howard Stern [WDM]
description:
Comedians in Cars Getting Coffee is an American comedy web series by comedian Jerry Seinfeld.

Episodes follow a format of Seinfeld introducing the classic car, driving to pick up the guest comedian, driving to a restaurant, and having coffee.
